name: Where my Money
description:
Where my money - this is a game where you have to collect as much money as possible, but if you suddenly want to sleep, then a cup of coffee will not hurt you!

I will leave the file for download if someone wants to make a mod for this game or something of their own using this code.

Also, if you are good at programming and want to help the project in development, you can email me: vladossk956@gmail.com
